{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a voluntary contribution fund for the UK armed forces",
        "additional_details": "We believe we all need to work together during these difficult times. We would like the Government to give the public a chance to give something back to the UK. We should be able to defend ourselves and have protection, and we believe we should give the public a choice to help so we can all stand together to deter any aggressor, as the public did during World War II.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to raise money for the UK armed forces by creating a fund where UK citizens can voluntarily commit to donating money to UK armed forces by a voluntary contribution each week or month from their pay or directly from their bank account.",
